CSCB07 Tutorial Exercise #1

This repository was created for CSCB07 Software Design Tutorial Exercise #1.

The purpose of this lab is to practice:
- using Git and GitHub
- cloning a repository
- compiling and running Java programs from the command line
- creating a Java class named Polynomial
- testing the Polynomial class using a Driver program

This lab includes work with polynomial coefficients, polynomial addition, evaluation, and root checking.
